# Bitninja Linux Agent changelog

# When adding an entry to the changelog, it should follow the established format.
# Any commented lines will be ignored when generating the changelog for the package.
bitninja (3.13.2)
    * SenseLog
      - Improved the CatchScrapersWith404 rule.​
    * WAF Pro
      - Fixes transparent proxy restart and signal handling
    * Bitninja WAF PRO - 1.0.9
      - Increased proxy_buffer_size values in nginx.conf
      - The service will not restart on Debian-based systems after updating.
    -- bitninja.IO team <packaging@bitninja.io> Mon, 08 Dec 2025
